###############################################################################
Entry project 2		Find the largest file in folder
			Classes: Python in The Enterprise
Author:			Grzegorz Kozicki
###############################################################################

Usage:

python list_dir.py [dir_path]


When no dir_path specified, lists content of the current directory.
The script prints files in the dir_path with corresponding file sizes.

If a file is a directory, gets recursively into each subdir calculating
the total size of all files existing in subdirs.
